www.karudaa.com

Karudaa.com is an online outlet which helps you to Send gifts to all Jaffna cities. Karudaa.com Deliver Gifts, Cakes, Flowers, Food items, Grocery Items and many more. 

They have great service, quality products and we trust them. We value a local relationship and the impact it has on our community.

– karudaa.com
